			<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
				Filling the gaps? Private sector response to the push and pull of the Indian public schooling system
			</h3>

			<p class="font-medium text-gray-400 mb-4">
				Kasturi Kandalam, Prashant Dewan, Sabyasachi Dey, Arnab Mukhopadhyay, and Soham Sahoo
			</p>

			<p class="leading-relaxed">
				We investigate how the private education sector responds to changes in public school quality and availability across India. Using state-level policy variations and household survey data, we analyze the dynamics between public and private schooling and their implications for educational equity and access.
			</p>
